name: _is_not_REAL
description:
_is_not_REAL 

A game where your main goal is to reach the EXIT 

You are allowed to make objects not_REAL through which you can pass .

BUT ALLOWED TO MAKE ONLY ONE OBJECTS not_REAL IN A LEVEL.

Type name of object (like FLOOR) TO MAKE THEM not_REAL 

CONTROLS:

A- LEFT D-RIGHT 

SPACE - JUMP 

W - GO TO NEXT LEVEL / USE 

CTRL - TO TYPE OBJECT NAME 

ENTER - TO MAKE OBJECT not_REAL (IF NAME TYPED CORRECTLY)

M - TITLE SCREEN

L - LEVEL MENU 

R - RESTART
